column2: "That's good, Zeno! A fight with you... I might be able to enjoy myself!"
"I don't believe I know who you are referring to."
"Tch, you sure do know how to ruin the mood."
"Later, Zeno! Hopefully you won't wuss out next time!"
"I'm fine, Echo. Sorry to make you worry."
"And you too, <%me>. Sorry I let you see me like this."
"This is my bad side. Do me a favor, and let me spare you the details."
"I need to go cool off. Later."
"<%me>, sorry, I'm going to run after him."
